Name: CFL
Title: Saskatchewan Roughriders at Hamilton Tiger-Cats
Desc: Week 2 comes to an end with the Roughriders (1-0) lining up against the Tiger-Cats (0-1).
LongDescription: Week 2 comes to an end with the Roughriders (1-0) lining up against the Tiger-Cats (0-1). Trevor Harris threw a pair of touchdown passes to lead Saskatchewan past Ottawa 31-26 to begin the season June 5. Saskatchewan beat Hamilton twice in 2024.
